				\begin{document}$$\:{\text{V}}_{\text{T}}=\frac{{\text{K}}_{1}}{{\text{k}}_{2}}$$\end{document}. To evaluate differences between non-denoised and DL-DN across dose levels, the bias % in AUC of TACs and in VT was quantified relative to the full-dose non-denoised reference. Logan graphical analysis [47] was also performed to generate a parametric VT image with an equilibrium time t* of 2 min. Images were assessed using RMSE and SSIM with respect to the full-dose non-denoised image.
